 sbfd
 redundant-sbfd
 
    
"dampening-secondary-wait": "integer", Secondary delay in milliseconds (default\n20000)
range: "1..518400000"
 
    
"enable": [ null ], Always set to true

    
"dampening-initial-wait": "integer", Initial delay in milliseconds (default 16000)
range: "1..518400000"

range: "60..3600"
 
    
"periodic-ping-disable": [ null ], Disable Periodic LSP Ping for BFD over LSP

    
"dampening-maximum-wait": "integer", Maximum delay in milliseconds (default 600000)
range: "1..518400000"
 
    
"multiplier": "integer", Specify the multiplier for BFD failure\ndetection
range: "3..10"
 
    
"bringup-timeout": "integer", Wait for session to come up in seconds\n(default 60)
range: "10..3600"
 
    
"minimum-interval": "integer", Specify the minimum interval for BFD failure\ndetection
range: "3..30000"
 
    
"encap-mode": "integer" Specify BFD Encap Mode on the tunnel
range: "0..1"
 
  }
}
